7.  Planned Changes to Improve Safety

As a result of the 12/16/04 compliance audit, Patriot Mining Company, Inc. will post written operating and emergency procedures at the field location of the storage tank.  Also, the truck used in the transfer of the ammonia has been parked and this procedure is no longer being utilized.  The tanks are being filled through the independent contractor supplying ammonia to the site.
